snippet.title: Obscure Games: Creatures PS1 (Part 1, Settling in)
snippet.description:
Here's a game that not many people should know about, Creatures for PS1! Unlike it's more well-known games in the series, this version plays very differently from the artificial life games, and lacks the complex elements of genetics and such. 

However, seeing as there is little to no commentaryless gameplay of this, and especially almost no gameplay that reaches to the end of the game I decided to start this series where I will play all the way to the end of the last world!
